 Получим тогда 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\ddot{q} & =-\dot{q}^{\wedge}\dot{\theta}-q^{\wedge}\ddot{\theta}+q\dot{\theta}^{2}-\dot{q}^{\wedge}\dot{\theta}+\lambda a\\
a^{T}\ddot{q} & =0
\end{align*}

