\begin{align*}
\ddot{q} & =\dot{\theta}^{2}q-U_{q}+\lambda a
\end{align*}

\end_inset

Дифференцируем связь
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
0 & =a^{T}\ddot{q}+\dot{q}^{T}\frac{\partial a}{\partial q}\dot{q}\\
0 & =a^{T}\left(\dot{\theta}^{2}q-U_{q}+\lambda a\right)+\dot{q}^{T}\frac{\partial a}{\partial q}\dot{q}\\
\lambda & =\frac{a^{T}\left(U_{q}-\dot{\theta}^{2}q\right)-\dot{q}^{T}\frac{\partial a}{\partial q}\dot{q}}{a^{T}a}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

Уравнения динамики
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
